msgid "日内回转交易策略（教学等价版）"
msgstr ""
"Intraday Turnaround Trading Strategy (Equivalent to Tutorial "
"Version)"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:3
msgid ""
"参考来源：`docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_09_日内回转交"
"易.ipynb` 第一个 Markdown cell。"
msgstr ""
"Reference source: `docs/_joinquant_migration_source/Example_09_日内"
"回转交易.ipynb` First Markdown cell."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:5
msgid "策略思路"
msgstr "Strategy and Ideas"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:7
msgid "使用分钟级价格计算 MACD；"
msgstr "Calculate MACD using minute-level prices;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:8
msgid "MACD 为正时加仓、为负时减仓；"
msgstr ""
"Add to your position when the MACD is positive and reduce your "
"position when it is negative."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:9
msgid "通过 `VS` 信号输出固定交易数量，形成日内回转风格。"
msgstr ""
"By outputting a fixed number of trades using the `VS` signal, an "
"intraday reversal style can be formed."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:11
msgid "诚实说明"
msgstr "Honesty"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:13
msgid "原始策略强调 A 股日内回转，但真实 A 股存在 T+1 约束；"
msgstr ""
"The original strategy emphasized intraday reversals in A-shares, "
"but in reality, A-shares are subject to T+1 restrictions."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:14
msgid ""
"本示例仅演示 qteasy 的日内信号处理链路，不等同于真实可执行的 A 股 "
"T+0 回转；"
msgstr ""
"This example only demonstrates the intraday signal processing chain "
"of qteasy and is not equivalent to a real executable A-share T+0 "
"turnaround;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:15
msgid "若需要贴近实盘，请改用 ETF 或期货标的，并校准交易制度参数。"
msgstr ""
"If you need to closely resemble live trading, please use ETFs or "
"futures contracts and calibrate the trading system parameters."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_09_日内回转交易.md:40
msgid "可执行脚本"
msgstr "Executable script"

